Package com.vangav.backend.networks.rest_client

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FutureResponse<T>
    FutureResponse is used to hold future response of asynchronous requests
    RestAsync
    RestAsync handles REST calls (GET/POST) with JSON/DOWNLOAD responses asynchronously
    RestRequestGetQuery
    GetQuery represents GET REST call's query (e.g.: id=123&name=john)
    RestRequestPostJson
    RestRequestPostJson is the parent class for a REST request's POST JSON
    RestResponseJson
    RestResponseJson is the parent class for a REST response's JSON
    RestResponseJsonGroup
    RestResponseJsonGroup holds pairs of (HTTP Status Code, RestResponseJson) in order to assign the correct response's holding JSON Class per response's HTTP Status Code
    RestResponseJsonGroup.RestResponseJsonGroupBuilder
    OPTIONAL builder pattern class for RestResponseJsonGroup to be used if a user wants to define responses for HTTP status codes other than the ones provided by the simplified constructors of RestResponseJsonGroup class (200 SUCCESS, 400 BAD_REQUEST and 500 INTERNAL_ERROR)
    RestSyncInl
    RestSyncInl has inline static methods for handling REST calls of different types synchronously
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RestSyncInl.RestCallType
